     H            Y.
     F** UEXR36D ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: EXSUB - GET MASTER# FOR TTAI              *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2020.10.15                       *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR36D'
     F*                    PARM           $SERL  18
     F*                    PARM           $MAST  20
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $SERL  18A  CONTAINER SERIAL#
     F*  OUT $MAST  20A  MASTER LABEL#
     F*      $RTN    1A  RETURN CODE (OK:BLANK, *:ERROR)
     F******************************************************
     FAB#WL7A IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $SERL  18
     C                     PARM           $MAST  20
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $MAST
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
      *
     C           $SERL     CHAINAB#WL7A              99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELEKMST#    $MAST
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $MAST
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           $MAST     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
